compactFile()→readFileSync,source.trim,minify,writeFileSync|minify single JS file via Terser (mangle:false)
beautifyFile()→readFileSync,source.trim,minify,writeFileSync|format single JS file with proper indentation
export compactProject()→walkJSFiles,relative,readFileSync,compactFile,minify,processed.push|compact all JS files in dir, per-file error handling, ret stats+savings%
